Application Description: Artistry Revealed: Peter Whyte, Catharine (Robb) Whyte and Their Contemporaries.This app accompanies the exhibition in celebration of the 50th Anniversary of the Whyte Museum, and shines a spotlight on the art of the founders, Peter & Catharine Whyte. View images of works in the exhibition ranging from drawings, sketchings and paintings, celebrating the place in the Rockies they called home.Read moreCollapse.
